  bold(b)_1 = (2pi)/a (hat(bold(y))+hat(bold(z)))",  " bold(b)_2 = (2pi)/a (hat(bold(x))+hat(bold(z)))",  " bold(b)_3 = (2pi)/a (hat(bold(x))+hat(bold(y)))
